  "text": "Potential kit contaminant OTUs were identified by the presence of negative Spearman's correlations between OTU abundance and bacterial burden (logged qPCR copy number), adjusted using Bonferroni corrected P-values < 0.05. OTUs subsequently of interest were cross-checked with a listing of potential contaminants [CITATION_1] .",
